    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a quintessential driver's specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain delivers linear torque through a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained for structural rigidity, including a proactive inspection of the rear subframe mounting points. Suspension kinematics remain sharp, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for precise turn-in. This example exhibits excellent mechanical health with a recently serviced cooling system and consistent compression across all cylinders, making it an ideal candidate for spirited B-road excursions.",
