    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior remains sharp, finished in a timeless coat that still holds a deep gloss, though minor road peppering on the front bumper and a few small stone chips reflect its honest history as a reliable commuter. Inside, the cabin is a strictly smoke-free environment featuring premium upholstery that has been preserved with care; while there is very light entry wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the rest of the seating, carpeting, and trim remain in excellent shape. All technological features, from the responsive infotainment system and navigation to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound and road-ready, having undergone a recent comprehensive inspection and a full synthetic oil change. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires have significant tread remaining, ensuring you are ready for the road ahead. This is a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a high-quality driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 31500.0,
