    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve shim adjustment and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul utilizing a high-flow water pump. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity remain excellent, making this a turn-key performance asset for the discerning enthusiast.",
